title: Highway Thru Hell S05E04 Wind Storm 720p HDTV x264
description:
Wind Storm  

Gale-force winds send a semi airborne and shut down the Trans Canada Highway. Al and Nick use two heavy wreckers to perform an Aldergrove Jelly Roll to get the semi back on its wheels and get traffic moving again. The storm wreaks havoc on Jamie's operation in Hope, leaving the office without any communication system. Al and Gord then have to recover a West Coast Fat Truck weighting 100,000 lb that had rolled down the embankment. The team use two heavy wreckers and a large excavator as dead weight to get the massive truck back on the road
